org.deeplearning4j.ui.stats

Class J7StatsListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.ui.stats.BaseStatsListener
      • org.deeplearning4j.ui.stats.J7StatsListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, org.deeplearning4j.api.storage.listener.RoutingIterationListener, IterationListener, TrainingListener

    public class J7StatsListener
extends BaseStatsListener
    J7StatsListener: a version of the StatsListener but with Java 7 compatibility

    Stats are collected and passed on to a StatsStorageRouter - for example, for storage and/or displaying in the UI, use InMemoryStatsStorage or FileStatsStorage.
